# Trivy vulnerability suppressions for time-series-analytics-microservice
#
# These CVEs affect Go libraries compiled into the kapacitor/kapacitord/tickfmt
# binaries (kapacitor v1.8.5, the latest upstream release as of 2026-05-06).
# They cannot be patched via apt-get; a new upstream kapacitor release is needed.
#
# Each suppression is justified by the deployment context:
#   - Only port 5000 (FastAPI) is published externally.
#   - kapacitord runs locally inside the container; port 9092 is never published.
#   - No Docker socket is mounted.
#   - No gRPC, Thrift, or Prometheus listener is enabled in kapacitor.conf.
#   - pprof is disabled (pprof-enabled = false).
#   - No email/mail parsing paths are reachable from untrusted input.
#
# Review when kapacitor releases a version newer than v1.8.5.

# CVE-2026-33186 [CRITICAL] google.golang.org/grpc v1.58.3 - gRPC authorization bypass
# Not exploitable: kapacitor exposes no gRPC listener in this deployment; the library
# is compiled in but never invoked as a server. No gRPC port is published.
CVE-2026-33186

# CVE-2026-33811 [HIGH] Go stdlib v1.25.9 - DoS via long CNAME in LookupCNAME
# Not exploitable: DNS lookups target only operator-configured, trusted OPC UA hostnames.
# No attacker-controlled DNS input path exists.
CVE-2026-33811

# CVE-2026-33814 [HIGH] Go stdlib v1.25.9 - HTTP/2 SETTINGS frame infinite loop
# Not exploitable: InfluxDB integration is disabled by default in kapacitor.conf.
# Kapacitor's HTTP port 9092 is internal-only and not published.
CVE-2026-33814

# CVE-2026-39820 [HIGH] Go stdlib v1.25.9 - DoS via ParseAddress/ParseAddressList in net/mail
# Not exploitable: no email-parsing paths exist in this service; SMTP/alerting handlers
# are not configured in kapacitor.conf.
CVE-2026-39820

# CVE-2026-39836 [HIGH] Go stdlib v1.25.9 - panic on NUL byte in net.Dial/LookupPort
# Not exploitable: this CVE is Windows-specific; the container runs Linux.
CVE-2026-39836

# CVE-2026-42499 [HIGH] Go stdlib v1.25.9 - DoS via consumePhrase in net/mail
# Not exploitable: same as CVE-2026-39820; no email parsing is exposed or configured.
CVE-2026-42499

# CVE-2026-41602 [HIGH] github.com/apache/thrift v0.17.0 - integer overflow in TFramedTransport
# Not exploitable: no Thrift listener is configured or enabled in kapacitor.conf.
# The library is compiled in but no Thrift server runs.
CVE-2026-41602

# CVE-2026-34040 [HIGH] github.com/docker/docker v27.1.1 - authorization bypass
# Not exploitable: no Docker socket (/var/run/docker.sock) is mounted in the container,
# and the Docker API is never called by this service.
CVE-2026-34040

# CVE-2022-21698 [HIGH] github.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.10.0 - DoS via InstrumentHandlerCounter
# Not exploitable: pprof is disabled (pprof-enabled = false in kapacitor.conf) and no
# Prometheus scrape endpoint is published or reachable externally.
CVE-2022-21698
